artmental moves support if you have questions about how oncall services can assist you please submit a helpsu request or call or 5 help 725 4357 services are available either in your campus office or at our offices on campus carry in services are performed by appointment and need to be arranged in advance rates see the client support rates page getting started services can be requested via helpsu last modified fri 18 nov 2011 at 17 26 pages about this service overview find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages service summary pdf champ campus hardware maintenance program contract support computer resource consulting footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
